The Principal of Government Day Secondary School Ruma in Batsari Local Government Area of Katsina State has reportedly been kidnapped by suspected bandits. Malam Sani Sa’idu was allegedly kidnapped on Friday after school hours around Ruma-Batsari road, the report stated. The Principal’s motorcycle was discovered by the roadside along Ruma-Batsari road after the purported abduction. A police report confirming the incident is being awaited.